#!/bin/bash

systemctl start apache2

metadata.startup-script:
#!/bin/bash
apt-get update
apt-get install -y apache2
echo "Hello from backend" > /var/www/html/index.html
systemctl start apache2

http_health_check.for_each: ${coalesce(lookup(each.value["health_check"], "protocol", None), each.value["protocol"]) == "HTTP" ? [{'host': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "host", None)}', 'request_path': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "request_path", None)}', 'response': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "response", None)}', 'port': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port", None)}', 'port_name': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_name", None)}', 'proxy_header': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "proxy_header", None)}', 'port_specification': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_specification", None)}'}] : []}

https_health_check.for_each: ${coalesce(lookup(each.value["health_check"], "protocol", None), each.value["protocol"]) == "HTTPS" ? [{'host': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "host", None)}', 'request_path': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "request_path", None)}', 'response': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "response", None)}', 'port': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port", None)}', 'port_name': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_name", None)}', 'proxy_header': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "proxy_header", None)}', 'port_specification': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_specification", None)}'}] : []}

http2_health_check.for_each: ${coalesce(lookup(each.value["health_check"], "protocol", None), each.value["protocol"]) == "HTTP2" ? [{'host': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "host", None)}', 'request_path': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "request_path", None)}', 'response': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "response", None)}', 'port': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port", None)}', 'port_name': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_name", None)}', 'proxy_header': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "proxy_header", None)}', 'port_specification': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_specification", None)}'}] : []}

tcp_health_check.for_each: ${coalesce(lookup(each.value["health_check"], "protocol", None), each.value["protocol"]) == "TCP" ? [{'request': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "request", None)}', 'response': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "response", None)}', 'port': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port", None)}', 'port_name': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_name", None)}', 'proxy_header': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "proxy_header", None)}', 'port_specification': '${lookup(each.value["health_check"], "port_specification", None)}'}] : []}

/Users/patrick/.terravision/module_cache.health_checked_backends: ${{for backend_index , backend_value in var.backends : backend_index => backend_value if backend_value["health_check"] != None}}
